<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<odoo>

    <template id="report_cooperator_certificate_document" inherit_id="cooperator.report_cooperator_certificate_document">
        <xpath expr="//h2" position="replace">
            <h2>
                <span style="color: #92C04A;">Certificado</span>
            </h2>
        </xpath>
        <xpath expr="//p[@name='certificate_generation_date']" position="replace">
            <span/>
        </xpath>
        <xpath expr="//p[@name='label_coop_number']" position="replace">
            <br/><p>En el libro de aportaciones al capital social de la cooperativa figura una 
            aportación obligatoria de 100 euros (cien euros netos) de <span t-field="o.name"/> 
            con NIF <span t-field="o.vat"/>, con dirección en Calle <span t-field="o.street"/> 
            y número de socio <span t-field="o.cooperator_register_number"/>, realizada el 
            <span t-out="context_timestamp(datetime.datetime.now()).strftime('%d/%m/%Y')"/> 
            en concepto de alta en nuestra cooperativa.</p><br/>
        </xpath>
        <xpath expr="//div[@name='total_table']/div/table/tr/td[2]" position="replace">
            <span/>
        </xpath>
        <xpath expr="//div[@name='board_commitee']" position="replace">
            <div class="row" style="margin-top: 8rem; margin-left: 18rem; width: 50%; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block; text-align: center;">
                <p style="display: block;">Valladolid 
                    <span t-out="context_timestamp(datetime.datetime.now()).strftime('%d/%m/%Y')"/>
                </p>
                <t t-if="o.env.company.bottom_logo1">
                    <img
                        t-if="o.env.company.bottom_logo1"
                        style="width: 80px; height: 80px;"
                        t-attf-style="{{ 'min-width: 100px; max-width: 250px' if report_type == 'pdf' else '' }}"
                        t-att-src="'data:image/png;base64,%s' % o.env.company.bottom_logo1.decode()"
                    />
                </t>
                <p style="display: block;">Energética Sociedad Cooperativa</p>
            </div>
        </xpath>
    </template>

</odoo>
